{"tid":1233880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐成晚 一天光就讓?","createTime":"2019-06-16T23:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:35:02.000Z","uid":76078,"like":2,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1f4a3fd3fe4f42dfb8727b6c67684e9ee7388b","tid":1233880,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:19:08.000Z","msg":"咁坐嚟做乜?"},{"pid":"e00d88a8783ed03bdadad72b5f9c6989dd282ef4","tid":1233880,"uid":93479,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:20:52.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課 - *CUP<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=cc5eff2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a>"},{"pid":"862e31dc8903f8ecd45924909584c0cae190067e","tid":1233880,"uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:21:47.000Z","msg":"二萬人就話<br />\n<br />\n但二百人<br />\n<br />\n快D變陣"},{"pid":"0c88034087207745b3b240503dd151fe82c1d439","tid":1233880,"uid":93479,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:21:50.000Z","msg":"警察搶民意高地<br />\n釋出善意<br />\n阻路責任就係我哋<br />\n最後去返佔中末期"},{"pid":"bbe80b9f29d6621acb387ba6cd0a80d22e42bf5d","tid":1233880,"uid":249965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:22:10.000Z","msg":"唔讓輸民意"},{"pid":"a31aed09fc2d76df7035a2fc49c04a004524abf1","tid":1233880,"uid":93479,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:22:11.000Z","msg":"2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。"},{"pid":"a9b35b64faa9ca01fcae08b300ef531bd739c24e","tid":1233880,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:40:35.000Z","msg":"拖到11點先讓唔得?"},{"pid":"15e4cc3ec472ee3ad222ad7ff21267344ebf6040","tid":1233880,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:49:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eac4e1b7e39fd12b38f2f5c2ff8769f849fef40e","tid":1233880,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:57:08.000Z","msg":"推 流動佔領值得學習"},{"pid":"ddfc5fd7cd6b37b28f9137e28816b36a3397242a","tid":1233880,"uid":149193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"一早叫你地番屋企抖"},{"pid":"9167a0da5246a707b243088fb7ec62f08d53b968","tid":1233880,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:57:53.000Z","msg":"有5個議員係度大家唔洗驚"},{"pid":"8744b6e76da213e324645d3a484e83254e515c99","tid":1233880,"uid":188671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:58:26.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=cc5eff2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。"},{"pid":"d7b3cae13f225a69c961fb6bd9213a470fffb534","tid":1233880,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n<br />\n後面出晒畜聾隨時圍上嚟<br />\n<br />\n死撚硬架"},{"pid":"b5fbed9f6c509330888cb497c8b34f102f6ea40f","tid":1233880,"uid":156582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:15.000Z","msg":"去禮賓府等齊人搵話事嗰個算帳好過<br />\n<br />\n對面出呢招唔讓真係冇著數"},{"pid":"5f67c155ea0a990184c8a5b9014c4117a9a0bf05","tid":1233880,"uid":93479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"野餐好多地方<br />\n<br />\n佔路一耐一定死<br />\n<br />\n唔好畀贏輸限死自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n我哋係要拎返香港，唔係拎條馬路呀<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"976402189a6e5f3bd846c9031c6dfe08096cc1e7","tid":1233880,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:00:44.000Z","msg":"我地要做既比到人感覺隨時可以再出黎佔<br />\n唔係實質佔，雨革話俾你聽鳩佔係冇用<br />\n把刀架起人質條頸有用過殺左人質好撚多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fd8630ecb4a58906c509716d9f29ee4e4f0857","tid":1233880,"uid":128522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"班黑警做緊公關show<br />\n後面夾上黎兩隊速龍出司有名<br />\n轉場或者散一散先<br />\n唔好被捕唔好受傷！"},{"pid":"4b86ea96ab238ff704b1663a3e76a977b12b8cfe","tid":1233880,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"狗射緊個波去我哋到<br />\n變到我哋係壞人 我哋阻住人<br />\n民意就會去翻佢嗰到"},{"pid":"709ea19d5c6131e88f4b92aa1e08b07080b56408","tid":1233880,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"人多就係唔讓姐 人咁少點唔讓 咁點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等議員慢慢講"},{"pid":"4372f4867d8a13854c67c23022c825e36681433d","tid":1233880,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"862e31dc8903f8ecd45924909584c0cae190067e","tid":1233880,"uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:21:47.000Z","msg":"二萬人就話<br />\n<br />\n但二百人<br />\n<br />\n快D變陣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"200個魚革本民前義士就話<br />\n<br />\n200個無乜GEAR無晒體力既, 真喺會被圍死"},{"pid":"32ded1577640fb209043648b3a1c41e0